    <abstract>
      <t>This memo describes version 1 of RSVP, a resource reservation setup protocol designed for an integrated services Internet.  RSVP provides receiver-initiated setup of resource reservations for multicast or unicast data flows, with good scaling and robustness properties. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
